Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.73,0:01:32.95,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(300,100)}in this secret, little room?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.69,0:01:40.07,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(300,100)}My memories embraced all mysteries and smashed them
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.07,0:01:42.95,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(300,250)}with quiet prayers I overcame my suffering
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.95,0:01:49.26,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(250,250)}and a new world began
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.26,0:01:54.84,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(0,100)}I didn't know whether men could accept the future
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.84,0:01:58.30,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(100,100)}like drinking wine
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.30,0:02:01.48,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}and threw all I had away
