Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.68,0:03:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, Sakai!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.18,0:03:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still groping girls' butts in battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.08,0:03:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,People don't usually sic their kid on their big-shot buddy either.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.18,0:03:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Futayo, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.65,0:03:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You're one tough cookie!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.77,0:03:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Father, could you properly introduce us?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.16,0:03:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, me? I'm Sakai Tadatsugu,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.01,0:03:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,the true leader of the Four Divine Matsudaira Kings.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.67,0:03:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Back in the day,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.84,0:03:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Matsudaira Motonobu was the school president and eternal student council president.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.10,0:03:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I was the chancellor and your dad was the commando unit's captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.72,0:03:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I was vice president, moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.83,0:03:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Ii was the vice president
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.23,0:03:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and Sakakibara here was nothing but talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.92,0:03:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.09,0:03:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I was the clerk and an expert in the humanities.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.08,0:03:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Girlie, isn't it time you overcame your athlete father's brainwashing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.21,0:03:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Girlie?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.43,0:03:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Care to join my academy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.42,0:03:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm dying to enroll someone like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.74,0:04:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Honda Masazumi's there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.36,0:04:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.45,0:04:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen Masazumi since middle school,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.26,0:04:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,but I heard she moved to Musashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.68,0:04:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't she the vice president?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.77,0:04:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,She sure is! So, why don't you enroll?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.51,0:04:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm honored by your offer, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.02,0:04:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it, Sakai.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.37,0:04:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Futayo is currently working as the colonel of the Mikawa Guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.67,0:04:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.69,0:04:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Colonel of the only Far East armed force approved by the Testament Union, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.92,0:04:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Intrigued?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.58,0:04:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.96,0:04:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Futayo is leaving Mikawa on a vanguard soon to ensure Musashi's safety
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.87,0:04:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,through the corridor to Aki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.45,0:04:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I told her she may do as she pleases once she reaches Aki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.14,0:04:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Meaning?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.12,0:04:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,My father and I agreed that I should decide everything for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.01,0:04:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Save the invitation until then, Sakai.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.02,0:04:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Futayo will accept if she feels she needs you or Musashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.40,0:04:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The world is ready for change
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.84,0:05:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and I want my daughter to make her own path.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.52,0:05:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.16,0:05:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Peerless Man of the East, Honda Tadakatsu's prized warrior is heading out
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.99,0:05:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,just as Peerless Man of the West, Tachibana Muneshige
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.16,0:05:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,is succeeding that name in Tres España.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.79,0:05:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Gah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.53,0:05:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Kazuno?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.92,0:05:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I see it's none other than Master Sakai.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.08,0:05:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Honda, you're still letting her live with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.48,0:05:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.18,0:05:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No one can replicate my wife's cooking
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.29,0:05:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,or swordplay quite like she can.{scene bleed?}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.98,0:05:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, she has perfect etiquette.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.73,0:05:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Judge.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.84,0:05:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I am currently teaching Lady Futayo the basics.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.95,0:05:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Futayo is a mature woman now,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.40,0:05:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,but Master Tadakatsu still tries to bathe with her
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.41,0:05:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,or take her to a grill.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.98,0:05:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He's most deplorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.03,0:06:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,His nickname "Dacchan" is short for "deplorable human".{well, shit}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.39,0:06:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not speak ill of Master Tadakatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.84,0:06:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Honda, she still has that demonic rule
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.43,0:06:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,where she's the only one allowed to insult you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.85,0:06:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Tadakatsu, it's time to prepare the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.40,0:06:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Judge, judge.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.56,0:06:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.15,0:06:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep up the good work!
