Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.83,0:06:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakakibara, tell me two things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.32,0:06:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me about Ii.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.08,0:06:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Does his absence today mean something happened to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.01,0:06:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's an automated doll named P-01s on Musashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.64,0:06:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,She boarded from Mikawa last year, so what's her deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.31,0:06:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakai, do you know about the spiriting away incidents called the "Lost Nobles"?{inconsistent punctuation inside/outside quotes}
