Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.87,0:07:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So, she's gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.46,0:07:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,A Tres España Inquisition Warship came in as they were departing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.39,0:07:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.58,0:07:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Tachibana Muneshige should be aboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.53,0:07:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,How exciting,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.77,0:07:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,although I'll never get the chance to see Futayo fight him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.04,0:07:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Tadakatsu, it is time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.19,0:07:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it. I'll be quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.98,0:07:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We will hereby begin preparing the fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.44,0:07:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, please commence your assigned tasks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.03,0:07:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Motonobu, things are proceeding as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.42,0:07:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll find out about the fireworks at just past eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.99,0:07:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But do you think he's okay with this, Kazuno?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.63,0:08:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Judge.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.57,0:08:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He was enjoying himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.71,0:08:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It was an appropriate farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.39,0:08:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.75,0:08:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand your thinking,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.02,0:08:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,but I shall serve you until the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.87,0:08:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Commence operations and watch the show as our lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.72,0:08:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Enjoy Mikawa's final fireworks, which will turn the world against us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.94,0:08:30.40,date 2,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\bord0\fscx102\fscy110\blur20\c&HFFFFFF&\fad(400,600)\an7\pos(215,650)}6:59 P.M. \N Kakamigahara, Mikawa
