Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.86,0:08:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!{fucking meidos}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.16,0:08:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,B1T3 to B2T3.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.28,0:08:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We're on duty, so no standing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.10,0:08:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see you from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.52,0:08:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.72,0:08:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.43,0:09:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I dealt with B2T3.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.41,0:09:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The results were favorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.52,0:09:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I dealt with B1T3. Same outcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.25,0:09:25.83,date 2,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\bord0\fscx102\fscy110\blur20\c&HFFFFFF&\an9\fad(400,600)\pos(1713,650)}7:44 P.M. \N Tea House Next to Sakakibara Manor
