Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.99,0:09:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Sakai, this is for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.25,0:09:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.19,0:09:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Sakakibara?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.43,0:09:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Judge.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.65,0:09:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Before he began working on the materials, he ordered me to deliver them to you, which I've now completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.74,0:09:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he forget something?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.21,0:09:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's blank!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.26,0:09:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.89,0:09:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Sakai?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.25,0:09:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Please pursue the kidnappers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.81,0:09:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.22,0:09:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe the Four Divine Matsudaira Kings will always be together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.95,0:10:00.62,date 2,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\bord0\fscx102\fscy110\blur20\c&H1E1E1E&\fad(400,600)\an7\pos(215,285)}7:51 P.M. \N Sakakibara Manor Study
