Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.97,0:10:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakakibara!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.88,0:10:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The master isn't in, so I believe he's finished his work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.61,0:10:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like to begin cleaning the room.{scene bleed?}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.39,0:10:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not you too, Sakakibara...
