Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.21,0:10:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.19,0:10:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Nenji!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.58,0:10:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet the chancellor had a hand in all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.47,0:10:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, what was he thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.11,0:11:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Water...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.65,0:11:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.58,0:11:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Who brought this chaos upon my town?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.31,0:11:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak now if you wish to say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.88,0:11:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.07,0:11:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Warning! Warning!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.50,0:11:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He made the girl with the cutest bangs in Musashi cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.05,0:11:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey! Chancellor and president!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.76,0:11:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this madness your fault?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.15,0:11:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You get the death sentence!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.15,0:11:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Over there...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.93,0:11:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Think there was an accident at the Testament Union's guard post?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.08,0:11:43.80,Title 3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)\bord0\fs45\fscx85\shad0\pos(600,693)\blur8\3c&H211E23&\c&H181518&}{\p1}m 0 0 l 249 0 249 54 0 54{\p0}
Dialogue: 1,0:11:38.08,0:11:43.80,Title 3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\bord0\blur0.8\fs42\fscx85\shad0\3c&H211E23&\c&HCAC7C7&\frx348\fry0\org(731,716)\pos(603,687)}{flashing on the shrine thing) - }Divine Contact
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.82,0:11:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't say.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.80,0:11:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried contacting the chamber of commerce, but I can't get through.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.22,0:11:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, let's break for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.23,0:11:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.10,0:11:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.46,0:12:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.25,0:12:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Behind you! Behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.20,0:12:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Behind me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.95,0:12:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,A girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.46,0:12:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sh-She's ghostly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.75,0:12:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.64,0:12:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't find Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.08,0:12:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.25,0:12:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It...{i think this is twice, but i can't tell since i have no audio}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.76,0:12:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a ghost!
