Dialogue: 1,0:12:29.01,0:12:32.64,date 2,,0,0,0,,{\fscx102\fscy110\blur1.6\1c&H899294&\an9\fad(400,600)\pos(1713,650)}7:57 P.M. \N In Front of Sakakibara Manor
Dialogue: 2,0:12:29.01,0:12:32.64,date 2,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\bord0\fscx102\fscy110\blur1\an9\fad(400,600)\pos(1713,650)}7:57 P.M. \N In Front of Sakakibara Manor
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.37,0:12:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kakamigahara Guard Post?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.40,0:12:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Honda?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.38,0:12:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You've sure gotten older if you couldn't dodge that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.04,0:12:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Slicing Dragonfly?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.43,0:12:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a Shinto weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.07,0:13:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that noise!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.10,0:13:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it coming from the ground?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.00,0:13:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's from deeper down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.61,0:13:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.56,0:13:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The Earth's plates.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.29,0:13:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it the Shin-Nagoya Platonic Plate Reactor?{weird name}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.62,0:13:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.32,0:13:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We're starting a meltdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.14,0:13:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You're what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.74,0:13:32.26,date 2,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\bord0\fscx102\fscy110\blur20\c&HFFFFFF&\an9\fad(400,1200)\pos(1713,650)}7:59 P.M. \N Shin-Nagoya Castle, Mikawa
Dialogue: 1,0:13:28.74,0:13:32.26,date 2,,0,0,0,,{\fscx102\fscy110\blur1.6\1c&H899294&\an9\fad(400,1200)\pos(1713,650)}7:59 P.M. \N Shin-Nagoya Castle, Mikawa
Dialogue: 2,0:13:28.74,0:13:32.26,date 2,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\bord0\fscx102\fscy110\blur1\an9\fad(400,1200)\pos(1713,650)}7:59 P.M. \N Shin-Nagoya Castle, Mikawa
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.89,0:13:34.00,date 2,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\bord0\fscx102\fscy110\blur20\c&HFFFFFF&\an9\fad(1200,600)\pos(1713,650)}7:59 P.M. \NCentral Unification Reactor, Mikawa
Dialogue: 1,0:13:30.89,0:13:34.00,date 2,,0,0,0,,{\fscx102\fscy110\blur1.6\1c&H899294&\an9\fad(1200,600)\pos(1713,650)}7:59 P.M. \NCentral Unification Reactor, Mikawa
Dialogue: 2,0:13:30.89,0:13:34.00,date 2,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\bord0\fscx102\fscy110\blur1\an9\fad(1200,600)\pos(1713,650)}7:59 P.M. \NCentral Unification Reactor, Mikawa
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.78,0:13:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That'll destroy all of Mikawa, not just Nagoya!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.29,0:13:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No one's left in Mikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.47,0:13:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just the automated dolls and us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.06,0:13:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you discover?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.48,0:13:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.28,0:13:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Our lord has only informed me that this is the beginning of the Genesis Project.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.12,0:13:58.83,spell,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\fs90\blur1.7\pos(1618.5,318)\c&HA38F7B&}{(brief flashback of the 10:33 typeset) - }Genesis Project
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.61,0:14:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The Genesis Project?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.29,0:14:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that it could potentially save us all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.80,0:14:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.80,0:14:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.28,0:14:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll bind me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.18,0:14:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Slicing Dragonfly can sever things from existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.72,0:14:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the Kakamigahara Guard Post burning...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.84,0:14:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I severed the guards' very existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.60,0:14:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Honda, why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.85,0:14:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Sakai.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.31,0:14:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have time to fiddle with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.50,0:14:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Kazuno and I have to intercept those Testament Union bastards.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.56,0:14:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Moron, they'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.28,0:14:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.19,0:14:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,My display of loyalty is to protect my lord's wishes and prevail.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.57,0:14:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So Tadatsugu, where does your loyalty stand?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.73,0:14:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you want to see what happens next?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.98,0:14:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So go, you no longer belong here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.76,0:14:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Honda!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.00,0:14:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What about your daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.55,0:14:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Honda!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.03,0:15:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.95,0:15:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We've reached a stop and shall begin turning back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.43,0:15:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluid output erupting from Shin-Nagoya Castle is increasing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.49,0:15:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Detection levels have increased a notch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.24,0:15:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Tres España's armed guard is taking action.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.87,0:15:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,A fleet of landing craft is approaching Mikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.44,0:15:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,K.P.A. Italia put our call on hold rather than blocking it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.48,0:16:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The Testament Union ships dispatched the Gods of War and commenced an assault.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.05,0:16:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Let them make their move.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.61,0:16:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.60,0:16:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,They'd use anti-aerial mountain gear for putting out a fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.32,0:16:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But if this was all just a feint...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.61,0:16:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't think Mikawa is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.68,0:16:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This way the Testament Union can force their armament into Mikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.90,0:16:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Futayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.22,0:16:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What would you have us do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.01,0:16:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Gather all officers on the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.78,0:16:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Judge!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.47,0:16:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Do as you like," eh, Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.00,0:16:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He wanted me to handle this myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.60,0:16:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What would Masazumi do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.90,0:16:52.19,date 2,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\bord0\fscx102\fscy110\blur20\c&HFFFFFF&\an9\fad(400,600)\pos(1713,650)}8:01 P.M. \N Deck Bow, Tama
Dialogue: 1,0:16:47.90,0:16:52.19,date 2,,0,0,0,,{\fscx102\fscy110\blur1.6\1c&H899294&\an9\fad(400,600)\pos(1713,650)}8:01 P.M. \N Deck Bow, Tama
Dialogue: 2,0:16:47.90,0:16:52.19,date 2,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\bord0\fscx102\fscy110\blur1\an9\fad(400,600)\pos(1713,650)}8:01 P.M. \N Deck Bow, Tama
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.63,0:16:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.11,0:16:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Have the fireworks begun?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.20,0:16:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Fireworks? Fireworks?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.64,0:17:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's no firework.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.09,0:17:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So, no fireworks?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.78,0:17:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Too bad, so sad!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.61,0:17:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Judge.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.20,0:17:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to get away from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.09,0:17:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And go where?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.65,0:17:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We might learn something if we drop by Blue Thunder.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.36,0:17:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.20,0:17:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,My power just went out!{oh cool, finally some mecha}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.00,0:17:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That light absorbs power if you touch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.99,0:17:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, how do we handle that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.34,0:17:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Notice from Base-1:
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.16,0:17:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It has been proposed that the Gods of War clear the way for the unit
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.05,0:17:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,ordered to destroy the Platonic Plate Reactor in Shin-Nagoya Castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.62,0:17:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But we're in anti-aerial gear!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.42,0:18:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We will send backup.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.66,0:18:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Tes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.64,0:18:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,A1 and A2 are to charge in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.33,0:18:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,A3 is to gather information and provide backup.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.62,0:18:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Tes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.73,0:18:13.15,date 2,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\bord0\fscx102\fscy110\blur20\c&HFFFFFF&\an9\fad(400,600)\pos(1713,650)}8:01 P.M. \N Prefecture Highway 79, Mikawa
Dialogue: 1,0:18:09.73,0:18:13.15,date 2,,0,0,0,,{\fscx102\fscy110\blur1.6\1c&H899294&\an9\fad(400,600)\pos(1713,650)}8:01 P.M. \N Prefecture Highway 79, Mikawa
Dialogue: 2,0:18:09.73,0:18:13.15,date 2,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\bord0\fscx102\fscy110\blur1\an9\fad(400,600)\pos(1713,650)}8:01 P.M. \N Prefecture Highway 79, Mikawa
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.17,0:18:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,One down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.68,0:18:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened, Zaragoza?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.94,0:18:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You're losing altitude!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.24,0:18:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,H-HQ, we were fired upon from the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.59,0:18:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,An automated doll fired at us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.39,0:18:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Kazuno from Mikawa's Honda clan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.54,0:18:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Horned witch!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.54,0:18:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Swords at my command!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.85,0:19:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,A shield before me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.05,0:19:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Increase numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.44,0:19:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Reform.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.89,0:19:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry it up! We're running out of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.01,0:19:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.74,0:20:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.70,0:20:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.28,0:20:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would the people of Mikawa trigger a meltdown in the Platonic Plate Reactor
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.27,0:20:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,when it could destroy the whole prefecture?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.44,0:20:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Muneshige, only Mikawa's locals know the answer to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.75,0:20:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll have to ask one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.95,0:20:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that pretty?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.66,0:20:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are these Lord Motonobu's "fireworks"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.66,0:20:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.14,0:20:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a man-made meltdown!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.00,0:20:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Our communications indicate Mikawa's automated dolls
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.22,0:20:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,are rising up against the Testament Union.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.81,0:20:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet Kazuno is leading the rebellion.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.28,0:20:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That means my father, Tadakatsu, is certainly involved in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.02,0:20:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Futayo, we could use this ship to aid Sir Tadakatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.18,0:21:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We must decide what course of action is most beneficial for the Far East.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.66,0:21:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Any opinions on this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.04,0:21:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.56,0:21:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If Mikawa intentionally started the meltdown,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.72,0:21:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,the Testament Union will revoke its position as{check timing}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.83,0:21:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,the Far East's representative and lay claim to Musashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.60,0:21:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,They would gain a great deal if they overtook the Far East and Musashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.79,0:21:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The worst-case scenario for us is the best-case for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.52,0:21:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're the only ones who can stand between Musashi and the Testament Union.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.53,0:21:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We had little contact with Musashi because we're from Mikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.41,0:21:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Futayo?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.47,0:21:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, we should stand by and remain completely neutral.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.99,0:21:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But doesn't that betray what's in your heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.04,0:21:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Judge.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.55,0:21:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Loyalty is only given meaning through one's actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.91,0:21:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.08,0:21:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Head of Communications, contact the Testament Union.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.56,0:21:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell them we wish to help in the event of an emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.46,0:22:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Judge!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.17,0:22:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Entering standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.25,0:22:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Await word from the Testament Union.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.73,0:22:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Got that? We're on standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.19,0:22:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Judge!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.04,0:22:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That night, our world began to change.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.79,0:22:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When I awoke this morning, I thought this world would never change.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.61,0:22:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The days I thought would last forever drew to an end,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.89,0:22:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}as we embarked on a journey with no return.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.37,0:22:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not that I knew that back then.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.98,0:22:54.72,ED-4,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1.6}I gather my dented courage and walk forward
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.72,0:23:03.15,ED-4,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,800)\blur1.6}because I swore to myself I would create my own future
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.76,0:23:12.92,ED-4,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1.6}Shower your light, O Star, upon the melody sprung forth here
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.92,0:23:21.77,ED-4,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1.6}and let me see your smile by my side
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.77,0:23:31.12,ED-4,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur1.6}I kept on calling your name even as pain stabbed my body
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.12,0:23:41.30,ED-4,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,1200)\blur1.6}I hope you will hear me some day, above the distant horizon
